<title type="html"><![CDATA[Safwan Ibn Asal al-Muradi (Radi Allahu Anhu)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=527&amp;p=569#p569"><![CDATA[
Safwan Ibn Asal al-Muradi (Radi Allahu Anhu)<br /><br />A Summarised comprehensive biography of Safwan Ibn Asal al-Muradi (Radi Allahu Anhu) is as follows:<br /><br />Name and lineage: <br /><br />Safwan Ibn Asal al-Muradi ar-Rabdi (Radi Allahu Anhu)<br /><br />Students:<br /><br />Zir Ibn Hubaish Al-Asadi, Abdullah Ibn Salamah al-Muradi and Abu Salamah Ibn Abdurahman Ibn Awf and other than them.<br /><br />Virtues:<br /><br />1. He participated in 12 battles against the kuffar with the Messenger of Allah (Sallalahu Alayhi Wa Sallam). (See Tahdhib al-Kamal 3/460)<br /><br />2. Abu Hatim ar-Razi said, &quot;He is a companion that settled in Kufah.&quot; (Kitab al-Jarh wa Ta'dil 4/420 - 421)<br /><br />Knowledge Of Narrations:<br /><br />There are 21 ahadith of his that are present in the Musnad of Imam Ahmad which he narrated or which have been attributed to him.<br /><br />Death:<br /><br />It is unknown. Radi Allahu Anhu<br /><br /><a href="http://www.salafiri.com/40-hadith-shaikh-ul-islam-imam-ibn-taymiyyah-hadith-no-21-the-virtue-of-knowledge-by-shaikh-zubair-ali-zai-1435h/" class="postlink">http://www.salafiri.com/40-hadith-shaikh-ul-islam-imam-ibn-taymiyyah-hadith-no-21-the-virtue-of-knowledge-by-shaikh-zubair-ali-zai-1435h/</a><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=59">Abu Ubaydah</a> â€” Sat Oct 22, 2016 7:16 pm</p><hr />
